7
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:44,176
Ya, Tuan ku.

8
00:02:44,210 --> 00:02:47,447
Kau mau sesuatu untuk mengurangi rasa sakit?

9
00:02:49,049 --> 00:02:50,717
